### ===== AUTH =====

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "raif", "password": "secret123"}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "raif", "password": "secret123"}

### ===== GAME =====

### Start a new game
POST http://localhost:8080/api/game/start
Content-Type: application/json

{"userId": 1}

### Get current game status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/game/status?userId=1

### Guess a letter
POST http://localhost:8080/api/game/guess
Content-Type: application/json

{"userId": 1, "letter": "e"}

### ===== WORDS =====

### Get a random word (admin/debug use)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/words/random

### Get words by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/words/category/Animals

### Get total word count
GET http://localhost:8080/api/words/count

### ===== STATS =====

### Get my stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats/me?userId=1

### Get leaderboard
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats/leaderboard